items.name: SudokuSolver
items.description: ♨️ A Java-based Sudoku solver app using Backtracking and Interfaces. Practice solving puzzles or let the app solve them for you. Includes sample puzzles and supports custom puzzle additions.

items.name: DiskUsage
items.description: ⚡Application, with parallel & sequential features, that calculates disk usage to help users understand system capabilities

items.name: facebook-clone
items.description: 🌏 Frontend & backend replica of Facebook using NextAuth,js, React.js, TailwindCSS, Node.js, JSON, & Firebase

items.name: JamGame
items.description: 🚗 Recreation of the famous game "Jam Game" with a UI crafted in JavaFX. It uses Java, Breadth First Search (BFS) for hints, and MVC architecture. The game incorporates car movement rules and dynamic puzzle loading, showcasing problem-solving and algorithmic techniques.

items.name: SecureComm
items.description: 👾 SecureComm is a command-line RSA encryption tool built in C# that enables users to generate key pairs, exchange public keys, and securely send encrypted messages. With intuitive CLI commands for key management and encryption, it ensures secure communication with robust validation and error handling.

items.name: Keyboard-E-Store
items.description: 🏬 Full-Stack online E-store system built in Java, Spring, Angular, & Typescript

items.name: RadixIP
items.description: 💡Application that constructs a highly efficient radix tree-based database, utilizing bit manipulation for storing IPV4 addresses

items.name: TradeSync
items.description: 🤖 A real/past-time trading simulator built with Java Spring Boot, OOP principles, multithreading, & WebSocket protocols. Features strategy backtesting & a flexible backend API for precise data transmission. The React UI, TypeScript, and TailwindCSS, showcases user trade history, account balances, & technical indicators

items.name: webfinvizapi
items.description: ✈ Finviz API web scraper application that scrapes any stocks financial data to help traders/investors with financial visualization

items.name: CipherPrimes
items.description: 👽 Prime Generation Library is a C# tool for generating secure prime numbers using parallel processing and probabilistic testing. Ideal for RSA, ECC, Diffie-Hellman, and cryptographic applications, it ensures efficient, secure key generation for modern network security.
